Traffic Accident Kills 17 in China’s Zhangjiakou, Xinhua Says

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-08-28T04:52:28Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-28/traffic-accident-kills-17-in-china-s-zhangjiakou-xinhua-says.html
At least 17 people were killed and
17 others injured in northern  China ’s  Hebei Province  this
morning, the Xinhua News Agency reported today, citing local
police.  The accident happened around 5 a.m. when a bus with 34
migrant workers rammed a semi-trailer parked at the roadside in
Shangyi County of Zhangjiakou city, according to Xinhua.  Editor: Ven Ram  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
